OL,3,CDevon Air Ambulance calls for more
OL,4,Csupport as fuel costs set to double
OL,5,Cthis year
OL,7,FDevon Air Ambulance has announced
OL,8,Fplans to take a funding case to
OL,9,FParliament, with fears that fuel costs
OL,10,Falone could increase by more than
OL,11,F#200,000 this year - effectively
OL,12,Fdoubling its current bill.
OL,14,FThe charity intends to highlight the
OL,15,Fgrowing financial pressures it is
OL,16,Ffacing in Westminster on Tuesday 2
OL,17,FJune, telling MPs directly about the
OL,18,Fneed for support to protect the
OL,19,Fservice.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
