FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780323077
OL,3,CDevon Air Ambulance calls for more
OL,4,Csupport as fuel costs set to double
OL,5,Cthis year
OL,7,FThis comes as at least 15 air
OL,8,Fambulance charities across the UK have
OL,9,Fwarned that the US-Israeli war on Iran
OL,10,Fhas more than doubled jet fuel prices,
OL,11,Fwith some warning that current
OL,12,Freserves could run low as soon as June.
OL,14,FDevon Air Ambulance is entirely funded
OL,15,Fby public donations but has warned
OL,16,Fthat it is operating in an
OL,17,Fincreasingly expensive environment,
OL,18,Fwith significant rises in aviation
OL,19,Ffuel, aircraft maintenance and
OL,20,Foperational costs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780323077
OL,3,CDevon Air Ambulance calls for more
OL,4,Csupport as fuel costs set to double
OL,5,Cthis year
OL,7,FThe charity is calling on MPs from
OL,8,Facross Devon to support a targeted
OL,9,Fapproach to reducing fuel costs for
OL,10,Fair ambulance charities, such as VAT
OL,11,Frelief or a rebate scheme - a measure
OL,12,Fwhich it says would provide immediate,
OL,13,Fpractical support to frontline
OL,14,Foperations.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780323077
OL,3,CDevon Air Ambulance calls for more
OL,4,Csupport as fuel costs set to double
OL,5,Cthis year
OL,7,FChief Executive Greg Allen said: "We
OL,8,Fare proud to provide a lifesaving
OL,9,Fservice for the people of Devon,
OL,10,Fdelivering hospital-level care at
OL,11,Fscene when every minute matters. But
OL,12,Fthe reality is that the cost of
OL,13,Fdelivering that care is rising
OL,14,Fsignificantly, particularly in areas
OL,15,Flike aviation fuel, and that presents
OL,16,Fa real and growing challenge for a
OL,17,Fcharity-funded service.
OL,26,@oD@bOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780323077
OL,3,CDevon Air Ambulance calls for more
OL,4,Csupport as fuel costs set to double
OL,5,Cthis year
OL,7,F"This visit to Westminster is an
OL,8,Fimportant opportunity to talk directly
OL,9,Fwith MPs about what that means in
OL,10,Fpractice, and to ask for their support
OL,11,Fin helping us secure practical
OL,12,Fsolutions that will protect the
OL,13,Fservice for the long term."
OL,15,FThe Exeter airbase sits within the
OL,16,Fconstituency of David Reed MP, who is
OL,17,Falso a member of the All-Party
OL,18,FParliamentary Group (APPG) on Air
OL,19,FAmbulances.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@[O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780323077
OL,3,CDevon Air Ambulance calls for more
OL,4,Csupport as fuel costs set to double
OL,5,Cthis year
OL,7,FAccording to Devon Air Ambulance,
OL,8,FDavid Reed has already pledged his
OL,9,Fsupport for the charity and visited
OL,10,Fthe Exeter airbase.
OL,12,FGreg Allen explained: "We're fortunate
OL,13,Fin Devon to have strong support from
OL,14,Fall Devon MPs, including David Reed in
OL,15,Fhis role on the APPG. His position
OL,16,Fgives him a valuable platform to help
OL,17,Fchampion the challenges facing air
OL,18,Fambulances and to ensure that services
OL,19,Flike ours are part of the conversation
OL,20,Fat a national level.
OL,26,@tD@WOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,437,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780323077
OL,3,CDevon Air Ambulance calls for more
OL,4,Csupport as fuel costs set to double
OL,5,Cthis year
OL,7,F"We're asking for cross-party support
OL,8,Ffrom Devon MPs to help make the case
OL,9,Ffor fair and sustainable funding, so
OL,10,Fwe can continue to be there for
OL,11,Fpatients when they need us most."
OL,13,FRepresentatives from the charity will
OL,14,Fjoin a national reception for air
OL,15,Fambulance services in Parliament on
OL,16,FTuesday, also using the opportunity to
OL,17,Frequest support for its longer-term
OL,18,Fvision, including plans for a new
OL,19,Fcombined headquarters and airbase.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
