OL,3,CDevon Air Ambulance calls for more
OL,4,Csupport as fuel costs set to double
OL,5,Cthis year
OL,7,FDevon Air Ambulance says that the new
OL,8,Ffacility would ensure it could
OL,9,Fcontinue to deliver a resilient, 24/7
OL,10,Fservice while advancing clinical
OL,11,Fcapability and meeting future
OL,12,Foperational demands.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
