CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1780323077
OL,3,CDevon Air Ambulance calls for more
OL,4,Csupport as fuel costs set to double
OL,5,Cthis year
OL,7,FElsewhere, air ambulance charities in
OL,8,FEast Anglia, Essex and Hertfordshire,
OL,9,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight,
OL,10,FLondon, Midlands, Scotland, Thames
OL,11,FValley, Wales, Yorkshire, Magpas,
OL,12,FWiltshire, North West, Great Western
OL,13,Fand Lincolnshire and Nottinghamshire,
OL,14,Fhave all raised concerns with ITV News
OL,15,Fabout rising fuel costs.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
